prompt: Good morning! I hope this message finds you well amidst what I imagine must be a bustling day of coordination and planning. I’m reaching out because I’ve got this upcoming business trip to Seattle—lovely city, isn’t it, with all that rain?—and I’m in a bit of a tangle. First and foremost, I need to secure a rental car, but I’m entirely at a loss about which companies operate there. I have a cousin who swears by the service at this one small outfit in Tacoma, but that’s neither here nor there. Could you perhaps compile a comprehensive list of all the rental agencies available within the city limits? Once we have that list, I’m terribly curious about fuel options. You see, I’m trying to be more environmentally conscious, so knowing whether each company offers electric vehicles or just the standard unleaded would be tremendously helpful for making an informed decision. And while we’re on the topic of the trip, I should probably cross-reference my schedule. I vaguely recall a few meetings scattered about, something about a ‘quarterly review’ and maybe a ‘client lunch.’ It would be splendid if you could sift through my calendar to find any events that might be relevant, just to ensure I don’t double-book myself for the car pickup. Thank you ever so much for your assistance!
